text: aelf is actively seeking partnerships with innovative technology companies, blockchain projects, and organisations focused on AI integration with blockchain, as well as, those developing blockchain use cases in Web2. We are particularly interested in collaborating with our partners to bring valuable developer opportunities to foster a robust developer ecosystem. Additionally, aelf looks for partnerships with projects that can enhance our platform capabilities through utility-based integrations, proof of concepts, and strategic initiatives aimed at increasing user adoption.
title: What partnerships is aelf looking for?
